  <!--
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    UNIVERSAL QUEST STAGE DEFS - Modular Thematic Actions
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

    These are verbs, not nouns. "A contact arrives" not "the pirate contact."
    Each stage is tagged so the selector picks the right ones for any pawn
    based on their current narrative profile.

    DESIGN RULES:
    - No plot-specific names or scenarios
    - Tags determine which stages a pawn gets, not which epic they're in
    - Every stage works for any pawn who scores high enough on its tags
    - Opening stages introduce; middle stages complicate; climax stages resolve
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  -->

